From least-cost to SDG-optimal sectoral allocation of Paris Agreement-compatible mitigation efforts
                    Dirk-Jan Van de Ven 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-9120-564X1, Clàudia Rodés-Bachs 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-6696-76851, Théo Rouhette 
